==Kaushik Shankar -- Home

~~~
{}{img_left}{Kaushik.jpg}{}{230px}{310px}

Welcome! This is the homepage of Kaushik Shankar. I was born and brought up in Chennai, a coastal city in Tamil Nadu, the southernmost state of India. I completed my secondary education at [http://davchennai.org/ DAV Senior Secondary School], Chennai. I attended the [http://iitb.ac.in/ Indian Institute of Technology Bombay] for pursuing my undergraduate study in Chemical Engineering. 

I am currently a 4th-year Ph.D. student in the [https://cbe.seas.upenn.edu/ Department of Chemical and Biomolecular Engineering] at the [https://home.www.upenn.edu/ University of Pennsylvania]. I am co-advised by [https://www.seas.upenn.edu/directory/profile.php?ID=24 Dr. Scott Diamond] and [https://www.seas.upenn.edu/directory/profile.php?ID=88 Dr. Talid Sinno]. I employ computational tools to predict patient-specific clot formation for my [research.html research]. 


